						 "written in C23; it's basically a fork of <a href='https://github.com/antirez/kilo' target='blank'>Kilo</a>"
						 " with <a href='https://www.gnu.org/savannah-checkouts/gnu/emacs/emacs.html' target='blank'>Emacs</a> "
